characterDescription.skinTone: light to medium beige with warm golden undertones and freckles distributed across the face, most concentrated around the nose and cheek area; some sun damage evident on forehead
characterDescription.eyeColor: hazel eyes with a predominantly brown center and an outer ring of green, with golden flecks visible upon closer inspection
characterDescription.eyeShape: almond-shaped eyes, slightly downturned at the outer corners, with a visible crease on the upper eyelid
characterDescription.hairColor: dark brown with subtle auburn highlights, particularly noticeable towards the ends
characterDescription.hairTexture: slightly wavy hair with natural volume and a soft, smooth texture; individual strands appear fine
characterDescription.hairStyle: long hair, parted in the middle, falling loosely around the shoulders; no styling is apparent
characterDescription.faceShape: oval face with balanced proportions and a soft jawline; cheekbones are slightly defined but not prominent
characterDescription.nose: medium-sized nose with a straight bridge and a slightly rounded tip; nostrils are moderately flared
characterDescription.lips: medium-sized lips with a slightly fuller bottom lip; natural lip color is a muted rosy pink
characterDescription.smile: closed-lip smile with slight upturn at the corners, indicating a genuine but subdued expression
characterDescription.eyebrows: thick, dark brown eyebrows with a natural arch; well-groomed but not overly shaped
characterDescription.ears: partially visible, medium-sized ears close to the head
characterDescription.cheeks: full cheeks with natural rosiness and a slight hollow beneath the cheekbones
characterDescription.facialProportions: balanced proportions with the eyes taking up a significant portion of the upper face; nose is proportionate to the face length
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: Numerous freckles covering the face, particularly concentrated around the nose and cheeks. There is a small, faint scar above her left eyebrow and visible sun damage on her forehead. Wrinkles below the eyes
characterDescription.overallImpression: natural, approachable appearance with a warm and friendly demeanor; face appears slightly tired but with a gentle expression
characterDescription.fullDescription: This woman is in her early thirties with light beige skin, extensively freckled across her face with the highest concentration around her nose. She has hazel almond-shaped eyes that appear slightly downturned. Her dark brown hair is parted down the middle and falls past her shoulders. A straight bridge leads to a slightly rounded tip of her medium sized nose, and her full cheeks create a soft curve in her oval face shape. The visible freckles and subtle auburn highlights in her hair add to her unique and distinct appearance, while sun damage on her forehead tells a story of time spent outdoors.
